        <ul class="nhsuk-body-s nhsuk-u-secondary-text-colour">
          <li>not designing services around technologies including not designing them around AI technologies</li>
          <li>checking for existing solutions includes existing AI solutions</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="nhsuk-body-m nhsuk-u-secondary-text-colour"><strong>January 2026</strong></p>
        <p class="nhsuk-body-s nhsuk-u-secondary-text-colour">Updated to follow GOV.UK with a small change to the intro paragraph to clarify this standard point (you need to provide the mix of channels that users need, rather than supporting all the channels all the time.</p>
      </div>

